summary_text: Kazuma, Aqua, and Darkness stopped by a hot spring.
Dust and Rin arrived at the slopes for some cold-weather fun. Unbeknownst to Rin, her friend had something important to tell her.
Megumin, Wiz, and Yunyun changed into their pajamas for a girl's night in. Yunyun could barely contain her excitement, but...
Cecily entered the casino to do some missionary work. At Aqua's request, Mitsurugi joined the efforts, causing Cecily to get a little off track...
Due to her lack of real-world experience, Iris expressed a desire to go places she'd never been. Chris decided to take her to a casino...
As Kazuma and company continued practicing for the big show, his passion as the hero of the story surged! A star was about to be born!
Amy and Mia took jobs as maids at a nobleman's mansion, but Mia's innocent recklessness might not be a good fit for the job...
Chris and Melissa coincidentally found work as maids in the same mansion. However, they both took the job with ulterior motives...
Yunyun visited the Crimson Magic Academy with Megumin. Amidst all the memories, Yunyun gave something to her cherished friend...
Cielo and Erika were practicing their dancing until Erika uttered a certain word that lit a fire under Cielo...
Lia forgot she was supposed to go on a quest with Kazuma's party. When he came to get her, she was still looking for the proper attire...
In the hall filled with exquisite food and bubbly, who would Iris choose as her dance partner?
Rin admires Melissa's calm and composed style, but a sudden encounter revealed an unexpected side to her cool demeanor...
Summer is a time for beaches and swimsuits! Darkness ran into a familiar face while shopping for a new swimsuit...
Aqua, Megumin, and Wiz went shopping for swimsuits. However, a comment from Wiz led to a change in mood for the group...
Chris and Dust snuck into a vault in search of treasure. This unlikely pair was in search of the same thing: a magic lamp...
Amy agrees to participate in a desert festival. To spice things up, she teams with Cielo to form a special dance team.
Megumin tries on her waitress uniform to help out at the cafe. For some reason, a strange glint appears in Cecily's eyes...
Mia has a new hobby: playing ninja. Despite Mitsurugi's bewilderment, Mia looks to show off her newfound moves!
Kunoichi are female ninja that slay their enemies from the shadows! Their activities include assassination, spying, and breaking hearts!
Aqua teaches Yunyun and Iris about Halloween as the town prepares to celebrate the lively festival.
Lia and Melissa take up martial arts to further enhance their beauty. During their training, Melissa teaches Lia what it takes to be a good woman.
Erika and Cecily use martial arts to improve their appearance. Erika is delighted at her cute outfit, while Cecily has other priorities...
Aqua shows off the outfits she made for Emilia and Rem. Along with Megumin, they try them on, although Megumin's fit is a bit loose...
Rin and Cielo attempt to become maids. The work is hard, but they each have their own reasons for making the effort.

Dressed in ninja garb, Kazuma and Lia were attempting to make off with a trove of monster-guarded treasure. Amazed by the custom-made ninja gear, Lia accidentally activated an enchanted light scroll...
Darkness, Iris, and Wiz were busily preparing for the party. As they worked, the more that "Santa" fellow Kazuma mentioned loomed large...
Yunyun arrives at a long-sought destination, an Arcanretian hot spring Megumin was raving about—where a familiar voice greets her.
Having heard of the exotic custom of "ice skating" from Kazuma, Chris and Erika give it a whirl. Catching on quickly, Chris shows Erika the ropes with an almost royal grace.
Ever the talented tailor, Aqua produces an entire furisode wardrobe for the gang. They eagerly prepare for a New Year's like never before.
The new year sees an abundance of street vendors lining Axel's roads. It is there Mitsurugi runs into Arue, who delivers an ominous message to the knight...
Erika comes across Amy, immersed in her pre-bedtime skincare routine. Hoping to reach new heights of cuteness, the idol begins to learn from the expert.
Iris practices making sweets under Lia's tutelage. Moved by the princess's determination, Cecily chimes in with some unique advice.
Amy asks Cielo to look after Mia for a night. The two pass the time with some stimulating girls talk.
Melissa visits Arcanretia's hot springs to get away from it all, but finds a familiar face awaiting her there...
The singing duo of Kazuma and Megumin share ideas for a grand self-introduction during their contest entrance.

title_text: Komekko Joins the Battle! Devilish Little Sister
summary_text: Komekko is hunting a pack of giant toads. When she finally finds them, she lets Hoost do all the work in taking them down.
Wiz and Mia dress up in martial arts gear to help promote Wiz's shop. Mia is certain she can attract customers, but...
Yunyun and Erika give in to Kazuma's request and put on the school uniforms, which they find to be surprisingly cute.
Dust visits Lia while wearing a school uniform, and tries to get her to take his jacket's second button. What is he up to?
Amy insists that Chris should teach her how to be a proper ninja...but why?
Aqua shows off her Hestia outfit to Bell, but Hestia is none too impressed. Just then, Ais and Darkness arrive wearing the same thing too...
The darkness of night is a ninja's friend. Black-clad Cecily takes Rin on a clandestine mission to deliver Order of Axis flyers.
Arue kindly agrees to join Komekko, who wants to stay up past her bedtime. That is, until Komekko suddenly nods off...
Mia and Amy are trying on festival outfits. Mia is excited for the upcoming festivities, but Amy has her doubts.
Mitsurugi offers to join Melissa on one of her treasure hunts. Just before entering the ruins, Melissa senses Mitsurugi's eyes on her...
Dust is once again busy losing everything at the casino, when he spots Wiz working the casino floor, wearing a strange outfit...
Arue is penning her novel at the beach. Iris is fascinated with her grand tale of adventure, and is eager to hear how it ends...
Erika invites Cielo to go swimming in the sea, but Cielo is not confident in the water, so Erika offers to teach her how to swim.
Chris and Mitsurugi are helping out at the grilled squid stall, but are starting to reconsider the division of labor with their so-called boss, Kazuma...
Yunyun and Komekko have a goldfish-catching contest while at the festival, but Komekko takes things a little too seriously...

title_text: Mel Joins the Battle! Lightning Girl
summary_text: The quest was a success, and although the group is growing tired of Mel's pranks, she is just getting started!
Rin and Amy attend the Crimson Demons' summer festival. While dressed in yukatas, they peruse the somewhat outlandish fare of the food stalls.

title_text: Vanir Joins the Battle! Masked Demon
summary_text: Vanir breaks with convention and joins Kazuma's group on a quest. Kazuma admires Vanir's battle skill and makes him an offer.
Kazuma and Lia are working at Darkness's family estate when Kazuma does something unexpected to an embarrassed Lalatina.
Mel was excitedly getting ready to perform another show with Axel hearts. On the other hand, Squall was doing his best to prepare for the inevitable antics of his mischief-loving roommate.
The town residents must have liked their costumes, because Aqua and Mia were having no trouble rounding up candy on Halloween. Mia wished wistfully that every day was Halloween, but...
Erika was struggling to write lyrics for her Halloween song, when suddenly, she hears Komekko singing and can't believe her ears!
Melissa was fawning all over Dust, who feigns indifference. He was excited for what looked to be the beginning of a long night, until reality set in...
Aqua made Kazuma and Darkness costumes in Ainz and Albedo's likenesses. Darkness is rather embarrassed as well as, in typical Darkness-fashion, excited at wearing the revealing outfit.
Rin and Mitsurugi both received outfits made by Aqua herself. But when Mitsurugi discovered Rin received her outfit for free, he finds himself cursing a very familiar name.
Megumin was searching for jewelry to match her new outfit, but Shalltear seemed to continue having trouble understanding the Crimson Demon sense of style.
Along with Vanir, Megumin and Yunyun dressed up in Santa costumes to deliver present. And ever-innocent Komekko sees her opportunity, and decided to tell Santa what she wanted that year.
Arue and Iris snuck in and left presents for the dozing Kazuma and Megumin, but discovered an egregious mistake when Kazuma and Megumin were opening their presents the next morning.
Mia and Komekko enjoyed playing in the fresh snow. Lia, watching over the pair for the day, played excitedly with them until their ravenous bellies started grumbling...
Vanir, Wiz, and Yunyun planned a mochi pounding performance in hopes of generating sales for the shop.
After an exhausting quest, Mel and Cielo were ready to share a nice, hot bath to relax and rejuvenate, but Mel's prankster spirit came bubbling forth!
With Amy in tow, Cecily was on her way to Samuidoh to recruit people to the Order of Axis. It's freezing, but that's no problem for Cecily, who swore her fiery passion would keep her warm!
Erika, Rin, and Komekko were having a great time making sweets together, but secrets came out as they discussed who they would give them to...
Wearing their old outfits from their lives in Japan, Lia and Mitsurugi began reflecting on their journey thus far. But both found themselves content in their new lives.
Melissa, who never takes a bet she won't win, was hesitant when Vanir suggested they visit the casino together. However, the wily demon had a plan to ensure victory.

title_text: Lolisa Joins the Battle! Newbie Succubus
summary_text: The two regulars arrived at the succubus cafe and filled out the papers, but there was still a long time until nightfall.
Chris, Darkness, and Komekko visit the Eris Church. Darkness tells Komekko an old story.
Rin and Cielo return from a quest wearing school uniforms. They sense the suspicious looks they are receiving.
Cecily captures a female guest's heart by showing her a play. But there's something fishy about this play….
Megumin and Yunyun invite Mikoto and Kurooko to the Crimson Demon Village. They have a great time talking about school.
Kazuma is welcomed by the maid and butler upon returning to the mansion. He senses something strange about the two devoted people….
Accelerator takes Misaka Sister and Last Order to a restaurant. Kazuma who just happened to be there, joins them…
Mia and Yunyun are excited after wearing native desert outfits. What does Mia say to Yunyun who is embarrassed because the outfit is too revealing?
Wiz and Lolisa visit a hot spring after getting some time off. But Wiz's vacation seems to have a purpose.
Megumin is in charge of cooking at the beach market. But Megumin's dishes are so bizarre that even Vanir is at a loss for words.
Mel and Komekko are enjoying fireworks with Kazuma. The two tomboyish girls seem to enjoy the fireworks in a flashy way as well.
Lolisa is tasked with customer service at the beach market. She is eager to impress Vanir, but her usual working habits keep on working against her….

title_text: <size=30>The Rising of the Shield Hero Season 3 Collaboration</size>
summary_text: Aqua and Raphtalia's parties get closer by wearing matching outfits. They decide to go eat at the restaurant together...
Iris sneaked out on a local festival day with Amy. The food Amy bought from the market was something that Iris had never seen before.
Melissa needs a way to sneak in somewhere, so Kazuma prepared a ninja outfit by Melissa's request... Who will be her next target now?
Explosion Goddess Lalatina reunited. One night, Kazuma overhears them talking.

title_text: Trick or Treat of the Mysterious Night
summary_text: Arue is interested in the Halloween festival held at Axel. She can't wait for the event to start.

title_text: Trick or Treat of the Mysterious Night
summary_text: Lolisa learning Halloween manners from Megumin. But it isn't that easy...
Maple and her guild members are diligently harvesting cabbages and lettuces. Sally and Kasumi do it easily, but Maple is having a hard time.
Komekko takes a closer look at the monster collection. She's seems particularly interested in the reindeer because...?
Lolisa came to meet Vanir wearing a cute Santa outfit. She is determined to help him promote his shop.
Yunyun, who is desperately wishing for a “friend” as her New Year’s first prayer, tries to offer everything she has after earing about the offering from Lia.
Kazuma receives a New Year’s Card from Cecily who is enjoying the New Year’s atmosphere. It seems there are a lot of stuff written in the card...
Megumin dresses and poses cool like Roxy. She asks Roxy to introduce herself but as a result...
Eris and Iris go on a quest wearing the same thing. Kazuma and Rudeus joins them just in case...
Darkness and Lia tries making chocolate. As a result, the counter top turns into a battlefield...
Megumin and Darkness can't hide their amazement after seeing the unfamiliar city of Tokyo. At that moment, someone calls them...
On the way to buy some crepe, Aqua and Wiz sees a long line in front of the shop. Aqua gets tired of the line that doesn't seem like it's going to get any shorter...

title_text: Claire Joins the Battle! The Escort of the Princess
summary_text: On her day off, Claire is planning to go on a quest with Kazuma's party. After hearing that, Iris says she also wants to join her...
Iris is contemplating if she should wear the Crimson Demon school uniform to the banquet. Even Claire can't admonish since Iris looks so adorable...

title_text: <size=34>Funifura & Dodonko Joins the Battle! Crimson Demon Classmate</size>
summary_text: Funifura was practicing her introduction before meeting Kazuma’s party. However, no matter how hard she tries, Dodonko can't memorize her lines...
Detectives club formed! Komekko and Mia decides to help someone in need. But let’s fill bellies first...!
Chris and Yunyun still has a hard time adapting to working as a staff in the cat ear tea house. They discover a cute cat when they went outside for a break.
New Comrade! Komekko gives a cookie to Lolisa who lacks confidence as a member of the detective squad…?

title_text: <size=34>Re: Zero -Starting Life In Another World! Collaboration</size>
summary_text: Kazuma met Ram and Beatrice for the first time. In front of the two women who speak harshly, it looks like he is discouraged a bit.

title_text: <size=34>Re: Zero -Starting Life In Another World! Collaboration</size>
summary_text: Rem and Emilia wearing the swimsuit prepared by Aqua. With Megumin's suggestion, they decide to play beach volleyball together.
Iris’s party relaxes at a hot spring. Coincidentally, they start talking about mixed-gender bathing.
Mia and Yunyun look for something. Mia heads to a skewer shop after catching its scent. Will they be able to find the lost object...?
Darkness and Lolisa have a conversation while taking pictures. Darkness thinks about how her pictures have been released, and falls deep in her own exciting delusion.
Cecily approaches Lia after her performance on stage. Cecily tries everything to make Lia the advertisement model of the Order of Axis.
Kazuma can't take his eyes off of Claire wearing her swimsuit. However, Claire is also looking at someone else.

title_text: The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya Collaboration
summary_text: Haruhi becomes delighted after experiencing another world's culture. She bring the unenthusiastic Aqua and Mikuru on a quest.

title_text: The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya Collaboration
summary_text: Megumin to Nagato who is quietly reading a book. For some reason, the conversation doesn't seem to go anywhere, but they connected on a deeper level.
You can’t write without a deadline. You eat away at yourself if there is a deadline. Arue is struggling every day while fighting against the deadline.
Lolisa and Komekko practice hard for the real thing. Megumin and Yunyun start reminiscing while watching the two of them.

title_text: I’ll cure you! Axel's Angel Squad
summary_text: Cecily works hard every day to evangelize the Angel Squad’s activities. The other members are barely able to stop Cecily running rampage, let alone do volunteer work.
Busy with their side jobs, the group has forgotten their original mission to defeat the Devil King. Aqua makes them outfits to get them back on track.
Kazuma, garbed in a warrior outfit, is raring to go, as he senses the chance to take down the Devil King and become a legend!
Legendary clothes require a legendary self-introduction—or so says Megumin. However, can Wiz mimic the Crimson Demon way?
Accompanied by Kazuma and company, a fired-up Chris made her way into the ruins in search of legendary treasure, but in a stroke of bad luck, she suffered a direct hit from a certain ability!
Iris and Yunyun wear the Legendary Adventurer outfit. Iris wants to learn something fitting to the awesome outfit…
Arue and Cecily obtain the Legendary Adventurer outfit. They talk to each other about their amazing effects…
Lia and Cielo try out a new stage outfit. Cielo is worried about Lia who plans to hang her outfit in her room before the performance...
The 3 members of Axel Hearts took a photo together for promotion purposes. But Erika doesn't seem to like the photo taken.
Dust and Rin try on the equipment they found from the ruin. Then, Dust starts praising Rin's appearance for some reason...
Vanir and Lolisa manages Wiz’s shop while wearing the outfit they got from investigating ruins. They are making good sales...
Komekko receives a special outfit as a reward for her work as a detective. She tells Megumin that she wants to go on a quest while wearing it but...
Do you want more power… Aqua was delighted to receive the forbidden magic item from Wiz. But it would cost something that Aqua liked very much….
After wearing the forbidden item, Wiz looks like the Ice Witch. Obviously, the power comes at a cost...
Megumin, who obtained an incredibly awesome outfit due to an item, fantasizes of her fancy future fanned by her younger sister...?
After her outfit changes with the power of the Item, Chris’s ability is enhanced. The moment he shackles the guard of the mansion he infiltrated with Bind, an unexpected event occurs.
Cecily wears a new outfit with the power of an Item. She tries to recruit passersby to join the Order of Axis right away but...?
Aqua and Darkness who were basically forced to change their appearance. They couldn’t let this go on and discuss a way to return to normal.
